			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "middle",
			"containerId": "ZnkYWWcODhwf4txo7ad8p",
			"originalText": "All users interact with the tables.\n\n1 row ⬅➡ 1 collection item. No\nhistory, latest value only.",
